look%20at%20you%20as%20a%20judge%20even%20when%20you%20lay%20down%20office.%20Therefore%2C%20things%20that%20are%20alright%20for%20other%20citizens%2C%20the%20society%20expects%20would%20not%20be%20alright%20for%20judges%20to%20do%2C%20even%20when%20they%20cease%20to%20be%20in%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20NDTV's%20Samvidhan%4075%20conclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshould-appointing-judges-be-more-transparent-dy-chandrachud-explains-7093491%5C%22%3EJudiciary%20Has%20No%20Exclusive%20Role%20In%20Collegium%20System.%20DY%20Chandrachud%20Explains%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%2C%20who%20retired%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20serving%20as%20the%20country's%20top%20judge%20for%20two%20years%2C%20clarified%20he%20was%20not%20casting%20an%20aspersion%20on%20judges%20who%20joined%20politics%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20for%20every%20judge%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20whether%20a%20decision%20that%20they%20take%20after%20retirement%20will%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20how%20people%20assess%20the%20work%20they%20did%20as%20a%20judge.%20If%20a%20judge%20joins%20politics%20right%20after%20his%20retirement%2C%20it%20may%20give%20rise%20to%20a%20certain%20perception%20on%20what%20was%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20his%20judicial%20work%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20politics%20he%20adapted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20role%20that%20the%20judicial%20institution%20plays%20in%20a%20judge's%20career%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20a%20former%20judge%20does%20-%20his%20behaviour%20or%20personal%20lifestyle%20-%20must%20accord%20with%20the%20sense%20of%20faith%20the%20society%20has%20in%20your%20institution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-australia-vs-india-alway