%20it%20undermined%20freedom%20of%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillie%20Walsh%2C%20IATA's%20director%20general%2C%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20slap%20in%20the%20face%20of%20travelers%20who%20want%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProhibiting%20all%20airlines%20from%20charging%20for%20cabin%20bags%20means%20that%20the%20cost%20will%20be%20automatically%20priced%20into%20all%20tickets%2C%26quot%3B%20Walsh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20an%20easyJet%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20low-cost%20carrier%20would%20appeal%20the%20decision%20and%20found%20the%20proposed%20sanctions%20%26quot%3Boutrageous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20our%20customers%20can%20bring%20a%20small%20cabin%20bag%20for%20free%20which%20gives%20them%20the%20flexibility%20to%20only%20pay%20for%20what%20they%20want%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Norwegian%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20also%20strongly%20disagreed%20with%20the%20decision%20and%20that%20it%20would%20follow%20up%20with%20Spanish%20and%20EU%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNorwegian%20is%20committed%20to%20providing%20safe%2C%20affordable%20travel%2C%20and%20our%20baggage%20policy%20reflects%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%20CEO%20Michael%20O'Leary%20labeled%20the%20fines%20%26quot%3Billegal%20and%20baseless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20such%20fines%20%26quot%3Bwould%20destroy%20the%20ability%20of%20low-cost%20airlines%20to%20pass%20on%20cost%20savings%20to%20consumers%20via%20lower%20fares.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20had%20instructed%20lawyers%20to%20immediately%20appeal%20the%20baggage%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVueling%20referred%20further%20requests%20for%20comment%20to%20the%20Asociaci%C3%B3n%20de%20L%C3%ADneas%20A%C3%A9reas%20(ALA).%20BI%20has%20contacted%20ALA%20for%20comment.%20Volotea%20did%20not%20immediately%20reply%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20consumer%20affairs%20ministry%20said%20the%20fines%20had%20been%20calculated%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Billicit%20profit%26quot%3B%20obtained%20by%20each%20airline%20from%20the%20sanctioned%20practices%2C%20which%20included%20charging%20extra%20fees%20for%20carry-on%20luggage%20and%20for%20reserving%20a%20seat%20near%20a%20dependent%20or%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20criticized%20the%20carriers%20for%20a%20number%20of%20other%20alleged%20issues%2C%20including%20not%20allowing%20cash%20payments%20at%20Spanish%20airports%20and%20requiring%20passengers%20to%20pay%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20fees%20to%20print%20boarding%20passes%20at%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20added%20that%20the%20airlines%20should%20cease%20carrying%20out%20the%20named%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airlines%20have%20two%20months%20to%20appeal%20the%20decision%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspain-fines-airlines-ryanair-easyjet-vueling-norwegian-volotea-2024%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732449334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6741efa09f2901eb60368644%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspain-fines-airlines-ryanair-easyjet-vueling-norwegian-volotea-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fines%2C%20which%20affect%20Ryanair%2C%20Vueling%2C%20easyJet%2C%20Norwegian%2C%20and%20Volotea%2C%20total%20179%20million%20euros%20(around%20%24187%20million).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspain-fines-airlines-ryanair-easyjet-vueling-norwegian-volotea-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20NCP%20thinks%20Ajit%20Pawar%20could%20be%20the%20next%20Maharas