.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20many%20reasons%2C%20I%20am%20concerned%20that%20what%20I%20am%20being%20told%20is%20in%20the%20trust%20and%20what%20is%20actually%20in%20the%20trust%20is%20not%20consistent.%20My%20mother%20isn't%20being%20forthright%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20transparency.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20simply%20want%20to%20know%2C%20as%20my%20brother%20does%2C%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20trust's%20content.%20Is%20my%20only%20recourse%20filing%20a%20motion%20to%20compel%20with%20the%20court%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoubting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Doubting%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20with%20your%20final%20question%3A%20Is%20a%20court%20filing%20your%20only%20option%3F%20Legally%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20yes.%20So%20far%2C%20your%20family%20has%20signaled%20that%20they%20will%20require%20compulsion%20from%20an%20outside%20authority.%20If%20you're%20pushed%20to%20it%2C%20hire%20an%20attorney%20who%20specializes%20in%20estate%20planning%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20the%20process.%20Things%20will%20likely%20go%20your%20way%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20conservator's%20legal%20and%20ethical%20duty%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20estate%20they've%20been%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20administering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20expectation%20of%20transparency%20is%20the%20bare%20minimum%2C%20and%20if%20your%20family%20decides%20to%20make%20your%20request%20as%20dramatic%20as%20forcing%20you%20to%20take%20legal%20action%2C%20it's%20a%20shame.%20If%20it%20comes%20to%20this%2C%20however%2C%20remember%20this%20was%20their%20decision%2C%20not%20yours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20speculate%20all%20day%20over%20what%20specific%20information%20is%20being%20kept%20from%20you%2C%20and%20your%20doubt%20about%20whether%20you're%20being%20told%20the%20truth%20over%20the%20content%20of%20the%20trust%20tells%20me%20you%20likely%20have%20theories%20of%20your%20own%2C%20but%20this%20isn't%20the%20mystery%20that%20needs%20solving.%20It's%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20mystery%20at%20all%20that%20must%20be%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20say%20exactly%20where%20your%20mother%20comes%20into%20things%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20your%20brother%20is%20siding%20with%20her%2C%20or%20if%20he%20is%20merely%20uncertain%20how%20to%20fulfill%20his%20role%20as%20a%20conservator%20since%20your%20mother%20is%20refusing%20to%20cooperate.%20You%20said%20you%20sent%20your%20brother%20the%20letter%20of%20demand%2C%20but%20it%20was%20your%20mother%20who%20isn't%20being%20forthright.%20Depending%20on%20who%20specifically%20is%20telling%20you%20%26quot%3Bno%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20have%20a%20few%20different%20suggestions%20for%20attempting%20to%20clear%20things%20up%20without%20going%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20brother%20is%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20problem%2C%20you%20can%20try%20talking%20to%20him%20and%20your%20mother.%20Explain%20your%20concerns%2C%20and%20offer%20them%20grace%20if%20there%20is%20something%20they're%20particularly%20stressed%20about%20you%20discovering.%20Try%20connecting%20with%20them%20beyond%20the%20estate's%20concerns%20and%20reminding%20them%20of%20the%20comfort%20and%20belonging%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20loving%2C%20harmonious%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20brother%20might%20be%20like%20my%20dad%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20conflict.%20He%20is%20an%20incredibly%20conflict-avoidant%20person%2C%20and%20he%20will%20put%20up%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20deprivation%20and%20abuse%20in%20exchange%20for%20peace.%20However%2C%20if%20someone%20he%20loves%20is%20paying%20for%20that%20peace%2C%20he%20always%20digs%20deep%20and%20fights%20the%20fight%20for%20them%20that%20he's%20rarely%20willing%20to%20put%20up%20for%20himself.%20Many%20people%20are%20like%20my%20dad%20%E2%80%94%20happy%20to%20sacrifice%20just%20about%20anything%20to%20avoid%20a%20fuss%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20it's%20their%20sacrifice%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20explaining%20to%20your%20brother%20how%20this%20situation%20affects%20you%20if%20you%20need%20your%20mother's%20cooperation%20as%20well.%20Communicate%20your%20needs%20and%20concerns%20with%20vulnerability%20and%20honesty%20so%20your%20brother%20understands%20that%20his%20choice%20affects%20you%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20brother%20understands%20how%20you%20feel%20but%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20your%20mother's%20forthrightness%2C%20try%20working%20together.%20This%20will%20mean%20going%20beyond%20long%20venting%20sessions%20on%20the%20phone.%20Instead%2C%20come%20up%20with%20a%20strategy.%20Split%20legal%20bills%2C%20support%20him%20as%20the%20conservator%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20your%20mother%20as%20a%20united%20front.%20Having%20someone%20to%20share%20the%20burden%20of%20this%20with%20will%2C%20if%20nothing%20else%2C%20bring%20you%20closer%20to%20your%20brother%20and%20make%20something%20good%20out%20of%20an%20otherwise%20terrible%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20or%20without%20your%20brother%2C%20though%2C%20I'd%20encourage%20you%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20thinking%20through%20the%20worst%20possible%20reasons%20your%20family%20may%20be%20hiding%20the%20details%20of%20the%20estate.%20Then%2C%20ask%20yourself%20how%20you%20might%20respond%20to%20those%20scenarios%20and%20what%20you're%20willing%20to%20forgive.%20If%20you%20can%2C%20try%20to%20reassure%20your%20family%20that%20you%20will%20respond%20to%20whatever%20dark%20secrets%20they%20are%20holding%20with%20grace%20and%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20behind%20the%20blustering%20obfuscation%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20fear.%20If%20you%20can%20love%20your%20family%20despite%20any%20financial%20failings%2C%20telling%20them%20so%20may%20give%20them%20the%20confidence%20they%20need%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20truth%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20ugly%20it%20may%2