rl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20ex-Meta%20employee%20and%20FIRE%20blogger%20explains%20how%20he%20used%20the%20'mega%20backdoor%20Roth'%20strategy%20that%20allows%20high-earners%20to%20bypass%20Roth%20IRA%20income%20limits%20and%20contribute%20up%20to%20%2469%2C000%20in%20a%20401(k)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223101%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andre%20nader%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740c4c5fa0140cdd564f5ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndre%20Nader%20resides%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20considers%20himself%20'semi-FIRE'd.'%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andre%20Nader%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndre%20Nader%20built%20a%20seven-figure%20portfolio%20by%20saving%20and%20investing%20in%20index%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20leveraged%20his%20tech%20career%20and%20dual-income%20household%20to%20maximize%20savings%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20strategy%20he%20used%20to%20max%20out%20tax-advantaged%20accounts%20is%20known%20as%20'a%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth'.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAndre%20Nader%20built%20a%20seven-figure%20portfolio%20before%20age%2040%20by%20following%20a%20few%20simple%20fundamentals%3A%20save%20a%20chunk%20of%20your%20income%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-millionaire-breaks-down-his-simple-investment-strategy-index-funds-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvest%20it%20in%20low-cost%20index%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20max%20out%20tax-advantaged%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helped%20that%20he%20worked%20in%20tech.%20He%20said%20he%20started%20with%20a%20modest%20%2440%2C000%20salary%20right%20after%20graduating%2C%20but%20eventually%20landed%20a%20high-paying%20job%20at%20Meta%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20won%20the%20income%20game%20by%20being%20in%20tech%2C%20by%20being%20a%20dual-income%20household%2C%26quot%3B%20Nader%2C%20whose%20wife%20is%20a%20designer%20at%20Uber%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20laid%20off%20in%202023%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20enough%20between%20her%20tech%20income%20and%20their%20savings%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20to%20find%20another%20job.%20Nader%2C%20who'd%20been%20writing%20about%20financial%20independence%20on%20his%20blog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fandrenader.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFAANG%20FIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202021%2C%20now%20writes%20on%20Substack%20full-time%20and%20does%20one-on-one%20FIRE%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-calculated-the-cost-to-retire-early-in-san-francisco-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early%3C%2Fa%3E)%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20high-earner%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3Bnaturally%20frugal%2C%26quot%3B%20Nader%20found%20himself%20with%20excess%20savings%20each%20month.%20When%20he%20was%20working%20full-time%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20used%20one%20of%20their%20incomes%20for%20household%20expenses%20and%20saved%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20thinking%20about%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20save%20this%20in%20the%20most%20efficient%20way%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20for%20many%20in%20tech%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20about%20taking%20advantage%20of%20those%20tax-advantaged%20accounts.%20Because%20when%20you're%20in%20those%20extremely%20high%20earning%20years%2C%20any%20amount%20that%20you%20can%20defer%20those%20taxes%20into%20the%20future%20is%20potentially%20extremely%2C%20extremely%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20particular%20tax-advantaged%20account%2C%20a%20Roth%20IRA%2C%20offers%20major%20benefits%2C%20including%20tax-free%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20an%20income%20limit%20that%20can%20prevent%20individuals%20like%20Nader%20from%20contributing%20directly%20to%20it.%20In%202024%2C%20single%20tax%20filers%20must%20make%20less%20than%20%24146%2C000%20to%20contribute%20to%20a%20Roth%2C%20and%20married%20couples%20filing%20jointly%20must%20make%20less%20than%20%24230%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENader%20has%20used%20a%20workaround%20known%20as%20a%20mega%20backdoor%20to%20sidestep%20the%20Roth%20IRA%20income%20limit%2C%20and%20he%20recommends%20all%20high-earners%20take%20advantage%20of%20it%20if%20they%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22828fd63b-d9aa-4281-966e-0052c75930b0%5C%22%3EUsing%20a%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%20to%20contribute%20up%20to%20%2469%2C000%20a%20year%20into%20his%20401(k)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20how%20a%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%20works%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20first%20understand%20how%20after-tax%20401(k)%20contributions%20work.%20Some%20employers%20offer%20an%20after-tax%20401(k)%20%E2%80%94%20Nader%20had%20access%20to%20one%20when%20he%20was%20at%20Meta%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20has%20one%20at%20Uber%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20save%20more%20after%20you've%20maxed%20out%20your%20traditional%20401(k).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20annual%20contribution%20limit%20for%20a%20401(k)%20is%20%2423%2C000%20for%20employee%20contributions%3B%20but%20the%20combined%20employee%20and%20employer%20contribution%20limit%20is%20%2469%2C000.%20Say%20you%20max%20out%20your%20401(k)%20and%20contribute%20%2423%2C000%2C%20and%20your%20employer%20contributes%20%245%2C000%20through%20the%20matching%20program%2C%20so%20you%20have%20%2428%2C000%20in%20your%20401(k).%20Since%20the%20limit%20is%20%2469%2C000%2C%20if%20your%20plan%20allows%20for%20after-tax%20contributions%2C%20you%20can%20put%20another%20%2441%2C000%20in%20after-tax%20dollars%20into%20the%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andre%20nader%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6734ff30192f52589858364d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENader%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20FAANG%20FIRE%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20works%20at%20Uber%2C%20and%20their%20daughter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andre%20Nader%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nader's%20wife's%20case%2C%20Uber%20matches%20up%20to%20%248%2C000%2C%20so%20after%20maxing%20out%20her%20401(k)%20in%202024%2C%20she'll%20make%20an%20additional%20%2438%2C000%20after-tax%20contribution%20(%2469%2C000%20-%20%2423%2C000%20-%20%248%2C000)%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catch%20is%2C%20while%20sitting%20in%20the%20after-tax%20state%2C%20any%20earnings%20you%20make%20on%20those%20contributions%20are%20taxable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20the%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%20comes%20into%20play.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20shift%20after-tax%20401(k)%20contributions%20to%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20or%20Roth%20401(k)%2C%20where%20it%20can%20grow%20tax-free.%20Not%20all%20401(k)%20plans%20allow%20this%20conversion%20and%20you'll%20want%20to%20understand%20your%20plan%2C%20including%20its%20restrictions%2C%20before%20making%20any%20after-tax%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nader's%20experience%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fandrenader.substack.com%2Fp%2Fmega-backdoor-roth-ira-401k%3Futm_source%3Dpublication-search%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecuting%20the%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20was%20working%20at%20Meta%20was%20quick%20and%20easy.%20He%20logged%20into%20Fidelity%20NetBenefits%20(his%20401(k)%20provider)%20and%20elected%20the%20percentage%20of%20his%20after-tax%20earnings%20he%20wanted%20to%20contribute.%20Then%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20do%20an%20in-plan%20conversion%20and%20selected%20the%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Bconvert%20after-tax%20contributions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20time%20I%20post%20about%20it%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20someone%20doesn't%20know%20that%20they%20had%20this%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nader%2C%20who%20has%20nearly%2025%2C000%20LinkedIn%20followers%20and%20specifically%20writes%20for%20FAANG%20(Facebook%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20Netflix%2C%20and%20Google)%20employees%20looking%20to%20achieve%20financial%20independence.%20%26quot%3BThis%20extra%20%2430%2C000%2C%20effectively%2C%20can%20end%20up%20in%20a%20Roth%20401(k)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20a%20super%20powerful%20type%20of%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recognizes%20that%20not%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20this%20strategy%2C%20nor%20has%20the%20funds%20to%20save%20%2469%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20a%20401(k).%20But%20if%20you're%20a%20high-earner%20who%20would%20be%20saving%20that%20money%20anyway%20and%20your%20plan%20allows%20a%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20really%20valuable%20for%20them%20to%20be%20aware%20that%20exists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-mega-backdoor-roth-ex-meta-employee-explains-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732447981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740c47bede4eeae392910a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-mega-backdoor-roth-ex-meta-employee-explains-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20working%20at%20Meta%2C%20Andre%20Nader%20used%20a%20strategy%20known%20as%20a%20mega%20backdoor%20Roth%20to%20max%20out%20tax-advantaged%20accounts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-mega-backdoor-roth-ex-meta-employee-explains-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marquee%20set%201%3A%20Teams%20splurge%20a%20whopping%20Rs%20110%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732447870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115626587%2Cimgsize-46462.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fipl-2025-mega-auction-marquee-set-1-teams-splurge-a-whopping-rs-110-crore%2Farticleshow%2F115626538.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IPL%202025%20auction%20saw%20record-breaking%20bids%2C%20with%20Rishabh%20Pant%20becoming%20the%20most%20expensive%20player%20ever%20at%20Rs%2027%20crore%2C%20joining%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20followed%20closely%20at%20Rs%2026.75%20crore%2C%20acquired%20by%20Punjab%20Kings.%20India%E2%80%99s%20star%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Rishabh%20Pant%20fetched%20a%20record-breaking%20Rs%2027%20crore%2C%20moving%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20after%20being%20with%20Delhi%20Capitals%20since%202016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fipl-2025-mega-auction-marquee-set-1-teams-splurge-a-whopping-rs-110-crore%2Farticleshow%2F115626538.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20South%20China%20Sea%20Dispute%20And%20India's%20Stand%20On%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20reiterated%20that%20it%20stands%20for%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20overflight%2C%20unimpeded%20lawful%20commerce%20and%20adherence%20to%20international%20law%20for%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Speaking%20at%20the%2011th%20ASEAN%20Defence%20Ministers'%20Meeting-Plus%20Forum%20at%20Vientiane%2C%20Laos%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20the%20upcoming%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20the%20regulation%20of%20maritime%20activity%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20needs%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20the%20code%20should%20not%20prejudice%20the%20legitimate%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20nations%20which%20are%20not%20party%20to%20these%20deliberations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20code%20should%20be%20fully%20consistent%20with%20international%20law%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20UN%20Convention%20Law%20of%20Sea%201982%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20believes%20that%20genuine%2C%20long-term%20solutions%20to%20global%20problems%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20when%20nations%20engage%20constructively%2C%20respecting%20each%20other's%20perspectives%20and%20working%20toward%20shared%20goals%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%2014th%20East%20Asia%20Summit%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20Meeting%20in%20Laos%2C%20also%20asserted%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubstantive%20and%20effective%26quot%3B%20code%20of%20conduct%20should%20be%20in%20place%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20with%20international%20law%20and%20should%20not%20prejudice%20legitimate%20rights%20and%20interest%20of%20nations%20not%20party%20to%20the%20discussions%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20Sea%20Lines%20of%20Communication%20(SLOC)%20passing%20through%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDISPUTE%20ON%20SOUTH%20CHINA%20SEA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20China%20Sea%20is%20a%20semi-enclosed%20water%20channel%20bordered%20on%20the%20west%20by%20Vietnam%2C%20on%20the%20east%20by%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Brunei%20Darussalam%2C%20on%20the%20south%20by%20Indonesia%20and%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20the%20north%20by%20China%20and%20Taiwan.%20It%20is%20located%20on%20the%20major%20international%20shipping%20route%20between%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20northeast%20Asia%2C%20including%20the%20ports%20of%20Korea%2C%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20Japan%2C%20and%20approximately%20USD%205.3%20trillion%20worth%20of%20goods%20transit%20through%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20annually%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20China%20Power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20China%20Sea%20also%20houses%20rich%20fishing%20grounds%20and%20over%20half%20of%20the%20world's%20fishing%20vessels%20operate%20in%20this%20area%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20BBC.%20Countries%20surrounding%20the%20water%20body%20have%20wrestled%20over%20control%20of%20the%20territory%20with%20competing%20claims%20for%20centuries%2C%20but%20the%20tension%20has%20grown%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20have%20staked%20claims%20on%20islands%20and%20various%20zones%20in%20the%20sea%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Paracels%20and%20the%20Spratlys.%20Though%20largely%20uninhabited%2C%20the%20Paracels%20and%20the%20Spratlys%20may%20have%20reserves%20of%20natural%20resources%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECHINA's%20CLAIM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20countries%20surrounding%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20China%20reportedly%20claims%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20largest%20portion%20of%20the%20territory%20and%20demarcates%20it%20by%20its%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bnine-dash%20line%26quot%3B.%20In%201947%2C%20Beijing%20issued%20a%20map%20detailing%20its%20claims%20and%20insisted%20its%20right%20to%20the%20area%20goes%20back%20centuries%20to%20when%20the%20Paracel%20and%20Spratly%20island%20chains%20were%20regarded%20as%20integral%20parts%20of%20the%20Chinese%20nation.%20The%20nine-dash%20line%20that%20appears%20on%20Chinese%20maps%20encompassing%20almost%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20includes%20no%20coordinates%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-pacific-13748349%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaiwan%20mirrors%20these%20claims%20and%20says%20South%20China%20Sea%20islands%20are%20part%20of%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDISPUTE%20ON%20CHINA's%20CLAIM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVietnam%20disputes%20Beijing's%20account%20and%20says%20China%20had%20never%20claimed%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20islands%20before%20the%201940s.%20Accounting%20to%20Vietnam%2C%20both%20the%20Paracels%20and%20the%20Spratlys%20have%20been%20actively%20ruled%20by%20it%20since%20the%2017th%20Century.%20It%20also%20claims%20to%20have%20documents%20to%20prove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippines%20is%20also%20another%20major%20claimant%20to%20the%20area.%20The%20Philippines%20invokes%20its%20geographical%20proximity%20to%20the%20Spratly%20Islands%20as%20the%20main%20basis%20of%20its%20claim.%20The%20Philippines%20also%20lay%20claim%20to%20the%20Scarborough%20Shoal%2C%20which%20China%20calls%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaysia%20and%20Brunei%20also%20lay%20claim%20to%20parts%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20that%20fall%20within%20their%20economic%20exclusion%20zones%2C%20as%20defined%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%2C%20or%20UNCLOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUN%20VERDICT%20AND%20CODE%20OF%20CONDUCT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20The%20Philippines%20turned%20to%20legal%20arbitration%20against%20China's%20claims%20over%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20On%20July%2012%2C%202016%2C%20the%20Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20in%20The%20Hague%20ruled%20overwhelmingly%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Philippines%2C%20determining%20that%20major%20elements%20of%20China's%20claims%2C%20including%20its%20nine-dash%20line%2C%20and%20recent%20land%20reclamation%20activities-were%20unlawful.%20The%20UN%20verdict%20was%20based%20on%20UNCLOS%20(United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea)%20-%20regarded%20as%20the%20global%20constitution%20for%20the%20seas%20signed%20by%20162%20nations%20including%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPredictably%2C%20China%20refused%20to%20accept%20a%20UN%20verdict%2C%20maintaining%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bnull%20and%20void.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bcode%20of%20conduct%26quot%3B%20(COC)%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20is%20being%20discussed%20among%20six%20countries%20-%20the%20Philippines%2C%20China%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Brunei%20-%20that%20are%20party%20to%20the%20maritime%20boundary%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBurma%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Laos%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Thailand%2C%20which%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20(ASEAN)%20along%20with%20other%20member%20countries%20--Brunei%20Darussalam%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Philippines%2C%20and%20Vietnam--%20are%20part%20of%20the%20negotiations%20for%20the%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20over%20a%20COC%20have%20waxed%20and%20waned%20for%20two%20decades.%20Last%20July%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20expedite%20an%20agreement%2C%20a%20three-year%20deadline%20was%20agreed%20to%20conclude%20the%20talks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowyinstitute.org%2Fthe-interpreter%2Fcode-conduct-won-t-solve-south-china-sea-crisis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Interpreter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWORLD's%20STAKE%20IN%20OUTCOME%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COC%20on%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20will%20affect%20India%20and%20several%20other%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Japan%20and%20Australia.%20China's%20claims%20threaten%20sea%20lines%20of%20communication%20(SLOCs)%2C%20which%20are%20important%20maritime%20passages%20that%20facilitate%20trade%20and%20the%20movement%20of%20naval%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20protect%20its%20political%2C%20security%2C%20and%20economic%20interests%20in%20the%20region%2C%20t