D%5C%221443%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Smith%20at%20his%20movie%20theater%2C%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%2C%20in%20Atlantic%20Highlands%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20Smith's%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%20is%20a%20shrine%20to%20the%20filmmaker's%20career.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELocated%20in%20Atlantic%20Highlands%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Smith%20often%20hosts%20events%20and%20introduces%20movies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20Smith%20at%20SModcastle%20about%20his%20most%20personal%20venture%20yet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEntering%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%2C%20the%20New%20Jersey%20movie%20theater%20owned%20by%20filmmaker%20Kevin%20Smith%2C%20is%20like%20approaching%20the%20altar%20of%20a%20giant%20shrine%20to%20raunchy%20slacker-cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGracing%20one%20wall%20is%20a%20mural%20of%20memorable%20characters%20from%20Smith's%20movies%2C%20like%20%3Cspan%3EElizabeth%20Banks%20and%20Seth%20Rogen%20in%20%26quot%3BZack%20and%20Miri%20Make%20a%20Porno%26quot%3B%20and%20Mark%20Hamill%20as%20Cocknocker%20in%20%26quot%3BJay%20and%20Silent%20Bob%20Strike%20Back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Posters%20from%20his%20films%20and%20live%20podcast%20events%20line%20the%20hallways%20leading%20to%20the%20five%20screens%20mazed%20through%20the%20building.%20On%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%2C%20a%20Kevin%20Smith%20movie%20is%20usually%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20Gen%20X%20movie%20fans%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20obsessed%20with%20Smith's%20signature%20low-budget%20artistry%20and%20unabashed%20embrace%20of%20R-rated%20antics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20first%20patron%20I%20see%20in%20the%20SModcastle%20lobby%20one%20Friday%20afternoon%20is%20a%20young%20boy%20of%20no%20more%20than%20six%20years%20old%20with%20his%20mother.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Smith%20walks%20through%20the%20door%20shortly%20after%20wearing%20his%20usual%20outfit%20%E2%80%94%20backwards%20cap%2C%20suit%20jacket%2C%20and%20shorts%20%E2%80%94%20he%20fills%20me%20in%20on%20a%20secret.%20Yes%2C%20SModcastle%20is%20a%20physical%20space%20devoted%20to%20the%20View%20Askewniverse%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20reference%20to%20his%20production%20company's%20name%2C%20View%20Askew.%20But%20there%20are%20other%20ways%20he%20keeps%20the%20lights%20on.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBirthday%20parties%20are%20one%20of%20our%20biggest%20moneymakers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20his%2030-year%20career%2C%20Smith%20has%20been%20called%20many%20things%2C%20but%20shrewd%20businessman%20is%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20Yet%20his%20artistic%20appeal%20has%20helped%20Smith%20turn%20himself%20into%20a%20viable%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20modest%20by%20design%2C%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%20is%20the%20latest%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20the%20grassroots-level%20hustle%20that%20propelled%20Smith%20to%20stardom%20with%20%26quot%3BClerks%26quot%3B%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a86580b-8634-4825-b6fd-62ca96bf1e4d%5C%22%3EFrom%20filmmaker%20to%20podcaster%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Smith%20mural%20at%20SModcastle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b9306a0a0cc14f223dcbb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221388%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mural%20on%20the%20wall%20when%20you%20walk%20into%20SModcastle%20Cinemas.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20released%20his%201994%20debut%20feature%2C%20the%20black-and-white%20comedy%20%26quot%3BClerks%2C%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20US%20indie%20film%20craze%2C%20when%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BPulp%20Fiction%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHoop%20Dreams%26quot%3B%20were%20showing%20audiences%20that%20there%20was%20more%20to%20see%20in%20theaters%20outside%20of%20what%20major%20studios%20had%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShot%20at%20the%20actual%20convenience%20store%20where%20Smith%20worked%2C%20Quick%20Stop%20in%20Leonardo%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20%26quot%3BClerks%26quot%3B%20introduced%20the%20world%20to%20wiseass%20New%20Jersey%20twenty-something%20characters%20like%20Dante%20Kicks%2C%20Randal%20Graves%2C%20Rick%20Derris%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Jay%20and%20Silent%20Bob.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20its%20countless%20pop-culture%20references%20and%20crude%20humor%2C%20%26quot%3BClerks%26quot%3B%20found%20instant%20acclaim%2C%20making%20Smith%2C%20who%20also%20played%20Silent%20Bob%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BIt%26quot%3B%20young%20filmmaker%20in%20the%20burgeoning%20indie%20film%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20went%20on%20to%20make%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BMallrats%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BChasing%20Amy%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDogma%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJay%20and%20Silent%20Bob%20Strike%20Back.%26quot%3B%20Though%20none%20were%20as%20universally%20praised%20as%20%26quot%3BClerks%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20doomed%20%26quot%3BJersey%20Girl%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20they%20built%20Smith%20a%20loyal%20and%20enduring%20fanbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dante%20and%20Randall%20at%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b80e3a0a0cc14f223dabb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22377%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrian%20O'Halloran%20as%20Dante%20Hicks%20and%20Jeff%20Anderson%20as%20Randal%20Graves%20in%20%26quot%3BClerks.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMiramax%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movies%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20most%20lucrative%20aspect%20of%20the%20Kevin%20Smith%20brand%3A%20himself.%20From%20a%20strain%20of%20marijuana%20to%20SModcast%2C%20a%20podcast%20he%20started%20with%20his%20former%20producer%20Scott%20Mosier%20in%202007%20(the%20%26quot%3BP%26quot%3B%20in%20podcast%20is%20replaced%20with%20the%20first%20letters%20of%20their%20last%20names)%2C%20Smith%20has%20been%20honing%20his%20public%20persona%20for%20decades.%20In%202010%2C%20this%20led%20to%20Smith%20finding%20a%20venue%20where%20he%20could%20perform%20in%20front%20of%20a%20live%20audience%20whenever%20he%20wanted%3A%20He%20called%20it%20SModcastle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20version%20was%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20at%20a%2048-seat%20location%20on%20Santa%20Monica%20Blvd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScott%20and%20I%20had%20just%20gone%20out%20to%20do%20a%20SModcast%20tour%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%20live%20whenever%20I%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20tells%20me%20while%20laying%20on%20his%20chest%20on%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20230-seat%20main%20theater%20at%20SModcastle's%20current%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20SModcastle%201.0%20on%20Santa%20Monica%20always%20sold%20out%20when%20Smith%20was%20in%20attendance%2C%20that%20was%20the%20problem%3A%20whenever%20he%20wasn't%20there%2C%20the%20place%20was%20empty.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20business%20model%20was%20far%20from%20perfect%2C%20Smith%20says%20it%20was%20the%20incubator%20for%20what%20would%20become%20the%20SModcast%20network%20of%20podcasts%2C%20which%20is%20now%20the%20backbone%20of%20his%20brand.%20Shows%20like%20%26quot%3BHollywood%20Babble-On%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJay%20%26amp%3B%20Silent%20Bob%20Get%20Old%26quot%3B%20were%20birthed%20at%20SModcastle%201.0%20and%20have%20since%20built%20loyal%20audiences%20and%20sold%20out%20live%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20finally%20closed%20down%20the%20Santa%20Monica%20SModcastle%20in%202011.%20Then%20in%202021%2C%20he%20learned%20of%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rent%20space%20in%20the%20same%20building%20as%20the%20Quick%20Stop%20where%20he%20shot%20%26quot%3BClerks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreat%2C%20we're%20doing%20it%20again%2C%20and%20it's%20right%20next%20to%20Quick%20Stop%2C%20where%20we%20know%20people%20come%20there%20as%20a%20tourist%20trap.%20This%20will%20be%20fantastic%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20recalls%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SModcastle%20hallway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b81b49b3250dbbcea0c59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hallways%20in%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%20are%20filled%20with%20posters%2C%20art%2C%20and%20photos.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20same%20problem%20that%20befell%20the%20LA%20location%20crept%20up%20in%20New%20Jersey%3A%20if%20Smith%20wasn't%20in%20attendance%2C%20the%20place%20was%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Smith%20and%20his%20business%20associates%20(including%20Ernie%20O'Donnell%2C%20who%20played%20Rick%20Derris%20in%20%26quot%3BClerks%26quot%3B)%20learned%20that%20the%20movie%20theater%20Smith%20used%20to%20go%20to%20as%20a%20child%2C%20Atlantic%20Cinemas%20in%20Atlantic%20Highlands%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20was%20going%20up%20for%20sale.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20kid%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20Atlantic%20Cinemas%20had%20been%20Smith's%20home%20away%20from%20home%2C%20where%20he%20saw%20the%20then-new%20releases%20like%20%26quot%3BRaiders%20of%20the%20Lost%20Ark%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20go%20on%20to%20shape%20his%20life%20and%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20instantly%20thought%2C%20this%20makes%20more%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20monetize%20every%20piece%20of%20this%2C%20I%20can%20show%20whatever%20I%20want%2C%20and%2C%20if%20I%20own%20the%20place%2C%20I%20can%20make%20a%20movie%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ab5da6a-99fb-41a7-822f-f755ab276eae%5C%22%3ESModcastle%20Cinemas%20is%20a%20home%20for%20all%20things%20Kevin%20Smith%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SModcastle%20Cinemas%20marquee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b7cd29b3250dbbcea0b89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESModcastle%20Cinemas%20shows%20first-run%20movies%20and%20Kevin%20Smith%20classics.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESet%20in%20the%20middle%20of%201st%20Avenue%20in%20Atlantic%20Highlands%2C%20the%20location%20has%20a%20deep%20history%20in%20the%20town.%20Smith%20tells%20me%20that%20in%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20the%20building%20was%20the%20stable%20for%20the%20horse%20the%20mailman%20used%20to%20deliver%20mail.%20In%201921%2C%20it%20became%20a%20670-seat%20single-screen%20picture%20house.%20By%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20Smith%20was%20a%20fixture%20there%2C%20it%20had%20two%20screens.%20In%201992%2C%20it%20expanded%20to%20three%20screens%2C%20and%20in%201999%2C%20it%20became%20a%20five-screen%20multiplex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Smith%2C%20SModcastle%20Cinemas%20is%20his%20grandest%20creation%20yet.%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20a%20place%20where%20he%20can%20show%20his%20movies%20anytime%20he%20wants%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20first-run%20theater%20where%20local%20moviegoers%20can%20see%20everything%20from%20%26quot%3BBeetlejuice%20Beetlejuice%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Robot%26quot%3B%20(the%20birthday%20party%20was%20there%20for%20the%20latter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20is%20the%20first%20to%20admit%20that%20he%20isn't%20raking%20in%20the%20cash%20showing%20these%20non-Smith%20movies%2C%20but%20it%20helps%20when%20he's%20not%20in%20town.%20And%20he's%20hoping%20that%20when%20you%20show%20up%2C%20you're%20buying%20something%20from%20the%20concession%20stand%2C%20which%2C%20like%20any%20movie%20theater%2C%20is%20its%20lifeblood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SModcastle%20hallway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b7f13a0a0cc14f223da75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHopefully%20the%20kids%20went%20to%20the%20right%20cinema.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20we%20weren't%20going%20to%20get%20rich%2C%20but%20it's%20simple%20math.%20If%20people%20are%20here%20watching%20a%20movie%2C%20a%20movie%20we%20will%20only%20get%20max%2050%25%20of%20the%20box%20office%20receipts%20for.%20Our%20only%20hope%20is%20they%20are%20going%20to%20buy%20some%20fucking%20snacks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care%20if%20you're%20here%20the%20whole%20day%20watching%20movies%20and%20only%20bought%20one%20ticket%3B%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20buying%20snacks%2C%20we're%20good.%20We're%20like%20the%20Catholic%20Church%3A%20we%20can't%20be%20picky%20anymore%2C%20we%20let%20everyone%20through%20the%20doors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20when%20Smith%20is%20at%20SModcastle%20that%20business%20really%20takes%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETickets%20to%20screenings%20with%20Smith%20in%20attendance%20or%20events%20that%20take%20up%20all%20700%20seats%20on%20the%20five%20screens%20are%20upcharged%2C%20with%20prices%20ranging%20from%20%2425-%2460%20depending%20on%20the%20event%20(a%20general%20adult%20ticket%20to%20a%20regular%20movie%20is%20%2411).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221270%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Smith%20characters%20on%20theater%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b7e0f9b3250dbbcea0bb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22953%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Smith's%20View%20Askewniverse%20characters%20are%20showcased%20in%20the%20lobby.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20also%20begins%20every%20event%20he%20attends%20by%20auctioning%20off%20memorabilia%20from%20his%20films%2C%20like%20an%20autographed%20%26quot%3BMallrats%26quot%3B%20script%20or%20a%20prop%20from%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BJay%20and%20Silent%20Bob%20Strikes%20Back%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20raise%20money%20to%20keep%20the%20theater%20in%20business.%20(Some%20items%20have%20sold%20for%20as%20much%20as%20%245%2C000).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building's%20historical%20significance%20also%20enabled%20SModcastle%20to%20became%20a%20non-profit%2C%20a%20move%20that%20Smith%20hopes%20will%20qualify%20the%20theater%20for%20grants%20and%20other%20financial%20support%20that%20will%20allow%20him%20to%20offer%20filmmaking%20classes%20for%20kids%20and%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20I%20meet%20Smith%2C%20he's%20introducing%20a%20screening%20of%20his%20latest%20movie%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%204%3A30%20Movie%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20SModcastle%20as%20the%20film's%20setting.%20The%20story%20follows%20a%20teenage%20boy%20named%20Brian%20(Austin%20Zajur)%20as%20he%20plans%20to%20sneak%20into%20his%20local%20theater%20with%20his%20friends%20for%20a%20day%20of%20movie%20watching%2C%20topped%20with%20seeing%20an%20R-rated%20movie%20with%20the%20girl%20of%20his%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20Smith's%20most%20personal%20movie%20in%20years%2C%20as%20he%20takes%20a%20pause%20from%20the%20View%20Askewniverse%20to%20tell%20a%20story%20that's%20a%20love%20letter%20not%20just%20to%20cinema%20but%20his%20own%20childhood%20at%20the%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHanging%20up%20behind%20the%20counter%20here%2C%20there's%20a%20note%20that%20Kim%2C%20my%20high%20school%20girlfriend%2C%20had%20written%20to%20me%2C%20and%20it%20says%2C%20'Dear%20Kevin%2C%20will%20you%20take%20me%20to%20see%20'Dirty%20Dancing'%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Highlands%20Twins%20Cinema%3F'%26quot%3B%20Smith%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20from%201987%2C%20when%20'Dirty%20Dancing'%20came%20out.%20Whenever%20I%20come%20to%20this%20place%2C%20that's%20what%20I'm%20reminded%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222302%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22letter%20to%20Kevin%20Smith%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b9380a0a0cc14f223dcce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222830%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20note%20from%20Kevin%20Smith's%20high%20school%20girlfriend%20hangs%20in%20the%20lobby.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20%26quot%3BThe%204%3A30%20movie%26quot%3B%20was%20predominantly%20shot%20in%20a%20theater%20he%20owns%2C%20Smith%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20costly%20location%20fees.%20But%20while%20the%20road%20to%20profitability%20might%20not%20ultimately%20be%20quicker%20(the%20film's%20financier%2C%20Saban%20Films%2C%20still%20has%20to%20make%20its%20money%20back)%20the%20connection%20between%20the%20movie%20and%20the%20physical%20theater%20is%20one%20Smith%20hopes%20will%20have%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20the%20profitability%20of%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20place%20fucking%20starred%20in%20a%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20demand%20to%20see%20it%20will%20diminish%20over%20time%2C%20but%20we%20own%20five%20screens%3B%20ain't%20no%20reason%20why%20every%20Sunday%20at%204%3A30%2C%20this%20can't%20be%20playing%20on%20one%20of%20the%20screens%20even%20if%20three%20people%20show%20up.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20passion%20project%20like%20SModcastle%2C%20Smith%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20power%20of%20nostalgia%20not%20just%20for%20his%20old%20movies%2C%20but%20for%20the%20ritual%20of%20moviegoing%20itself.%20Along%20with%20showing%20his%20own%20movies%2C%20Smith%20is%20booking%20hard-to-find%20titles%20to%20screen%20in%20hopes%20that%20the%20theater%20becomes%20a%20destination%20for%20cinephiles.%20He%20also%20offers%20his%20screens%20to%20filmmakers%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20out%20a%20showtime%2C%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20%26quot%3Bfour-walling%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20show%20the%20movies%20they%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kids%20sitting%20in%20movie%20theater%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b82db01ea6d83dee406f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Smith's%20%26quot%3BThe%204%3A30%20Movie.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESaban%20Films%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20leave%20SModcastle%2C%20the%20birthday%20party%20has%20ended%2C%20and%20there's%20already%20a%20line%20stretching%20down%20the%20block%20for%20that%20evening's%20screening.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20and%20I%20part%20ways%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%20and%20he%20goes%20over%20to%20say%20hello%20and%20take%20selfies%20with%20some%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20reminds%20me%20of%20something%20he%20told%20me%20earlier%3A%20Yes%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20Kevin%20Smith%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20never%20not%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20place%20is%20packed%2C%20you%20feel%20accomplished%20as%20fuck%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20looking%20around%20a%20theater%20that%20was%20so%20important%20to%20him%20early%20in%20life.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20always%20a%20struggle%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be.%20Because%20if%20it%20wasn't%2C%20what%20you're%20saying%20is%20I%20deserve%20money%20to%20make%20pretend%20for%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-smith-smodcastle-movie-theater-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732447081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740ff5dede4eeae3929268a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-smith-smodcastle-movie-theater-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kevin%20Smith%20turned%20the%20movie%20theater%20he%20grew%20up%20going%20to%20into%20a%20shrine%20to%20his%20filmography.%20It's%20also%20the%20setting%20of%20his%20latest%20movie%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%204%3A30%20movie.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-smith-smodcastle-movie-theater-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Dead%2C%20Over%2030%20Cops%20Injured%3A%20Violence%20In%20UP's%20Sambhal%20Over%20Mosque%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChaos%20erupted%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Sambhal%20this%20morning%20as%20a%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Jama%20Masjid%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes%20between%20locals%20and%20police%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20three%20individuals.%20The%20mosque%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20contentious%20legal%20battle%20over%20claims%20that%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20violence%20began%20when%20a%20crowd%20gathered%20near%20the%20mosque%20as%20the%20survey%20team%2C%20led%20by%20an%20%26quot%3BAdvocate%20Commissioner%2C%26quot%3B%20began%20its%20work.%20The%20crowd%20swelled%20to%20nearly%20a%20thousand%20people%2C%20who%20tried%20to%20prevent%20the%20police%20from%20entering%20the%20mosque.%20Some%20individuals%20in%20the%20crowd%20threw%20stones%20at%20police%20personnel%20stationed%20at%20the%20site.%20The%20mob%20set%20more%20than%20ten%20vehicles%20on%20fire.%20The%20police%20responded%20with%20tear%20gas%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob.%20In%20the%20ensuing%20chaos%2C%20two%20individuals%20were%20killed%20and%20over%2030%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20people%20identified%20as%20Naeem%2C%20Bilal%20and%20Nauman%20have%20been%20killed.%20Some%20policemen%20including%20the%20gunner%20of%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20have%20also%20been%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20Moradabad%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20Aunjaneya%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20which%20began%20at%207%3A30%20am%2C%20was%20part%20of%20a%20process%20initiated%20by%20a%20petition%20claiming%20that%20a%20temple%20once%20stood%20where%20the%20mosque%20now%20stands.%20Tensions%20have%20been%20simmering%20in%20Sambhal%20since%20a%20similar%20survey%20was%20conducted%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20historical%20texts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBaburnama%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAin-e-Akbari%26quot%3B%20document%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Mughal%20emperor%20Babur%20in%201529.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20the%20survey%20argue%20it%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20in%20uncovering%20historical%20truths%2C%20while%20critics%20view%20it%20as%20a%20provocation%20that%20violates%20the%20sanctity%20of%20religious%20places%20as%20upheld%20by%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20individuals%20in%20the%20crowd%20threw%20stones%20at%20the%20police%20team.%20The%20police%20used%20minor%20force%20and%20tear%20gas%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%20Those%20involved%20in%20the%20violence%20will%20be%20identified%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Krishna%20Kumar%20Vishnoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Moradabad%20Police%20Commissioner%20Ananjay%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%2015%20people%2C%20including%20three%20women%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%20Videos%20circulating%20online%20purportedly%20show%20the%20throwing%20of%20stones%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20and%20several%20vehicles%20parked%20in%20the%20vicinity%20were%20reportedly%20set%20ablaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20unrest%2C%20officials%20completed%20the%20survey%20as%20planned.%20Advocate%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%20stated%20that%20the%20survey%20team%20conducted%20a%20detailed%20examination%20of%20the%20site%2C%20supported%20by%20videography%20and%20photography%20as%20per%20the%20court's%20directives.%20The%20survey%20report%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20submitted%20by%20November%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20political%20and%20community%20reactions.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20of%20orchestrating%20the%20unrest%20to%20distract%20from%20allegations%20of%20electoral%20malpractice%20in%20recent%20bypolls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20serious%20incident%20occurred%20in%20Sambhal.%20A%20survey%20team%20was%20deliberately%20sent%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20disrupt%20discussions%20about%20the%20elections.%20The%20intention%20was%20to%20create%20chaos%20so%20that%20no%20debate%20on%20election%20issues%20could%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%9B%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%87%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%81%E0