A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20accounting%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20is%20turning%20to%20technology%20to%20improve%20its%20recruiting%20process%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20by%20allowing%20job%20candidates%20to%20warm%20up%20with%20an%20AI%20interviewer%20before%20getting%20face-to-face%20with%20a%20real%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20leaders%20who%20work%20on%20recruiting%20and%20metaverse%20experiences%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20AI%20interviewer%20was%20aimed%20at%20providing%20a%20better%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20less%20stressful%20%E2%80%94%20hiring%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20link%20to%20the%20AI-powered%20avatar%2C%20called%20eVe%2C%20is%20sent%20out%20to%20candidates%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20are%20selected%20to%20advance%20to%20the%20interview%20stage.%20eVe%20can%20answer%20questions%20about%20the%20company%20and%20help%20candidates%20prepare%20for%20their%20interview%20with%20a%20real%20person%2C%20according%20to%20Francesca%20Jones%2C%20an%20early%20careers%20leader%20at%20EY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20avatar%2C%20which%20appears%20on%20the%20screen%20as%20a%20real%20person%20would%20during%20a%20video%20chat%2C%20can%20be%20spoken%20to%20directly%20and%20offers%20verbal%20answers%20back%20within%20moments%2C%20mimicking%20an%20actual%20conversation.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20used%20with%20text%20like%20other%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EeVe%20can%20walk%20candidates%20through%20what%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-graduate-hires-start-dates-delayed-slowdown-strategy-consulting-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEY%20hiring%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20like%20and%20help%20with%20case%20study%20preparation.%20It%20can%20also%20answer%20follow-up%20questions%20and%20give%20detailed%20responses%20about%20how%20benefits%20like%20healthcare%20and%20retirement%20plans%20work%20at%20the%20company.%20eVe%20can%20be%20used%20at%20any%20point%20in%20the%20process%2C%20so%20candidates%20can%20revisit%20it%20when%20weighing%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20accept%20a%20job%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpartner-pay-at-big-four-falling-ey-pwc-deloitte-kpmg-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEY%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20offering%20eVe%20to%20job%20candidates%20in%20early%20October%2C%20so%20they%20are%20still%20waiting%20to%20get%20a%20fuller%20picture%20of%20how%20it%20is%20being%20used.%20However%2C%20eVe%20went%20through%20months%20of%20internal%20user%20testing%20with%20hundreds%20of%20interns%2C%20which%20gave%20a%20glimpse%20into%20how%20early-career%20professionals%20in%20particular%20would%20use%20the%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20types%20of%20questions%20they%20asked%20and%20how%20much%20time%20they%20actually%20spent%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Domhnaill%20Hernon%2C%20global%20lead%20of%20EY's%20Metaverse%20Lab%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20suspected%20the%20younger%20generation%20might%20spend%20two%20to%20three%20minutes%20with%20eVe%20and%20then%20move%20on%2C%20but%20they%20were%20regularly%20spending%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20engaging%20with%20it%20conversationally%2C%20asking%20questions%20and%20follow-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20intern%20who%20spent%2025%20minutes%20talking%20to%20eVe%20went%20into%20extreme%20detail%20evaluating%20EY's%20compensation%20benefits%2C%20particularly%20comparing%20the%20company's%20pension%20plan%20to%20its%20401K%20offering.%20Others%20asked%20the%20sort%20of%20questions%20that%20many%20early-career%20professionals%20want%20to%20know%20ahead%20of%20interviews%20but%20might%20be%20afraid%20to%20ask%2C%20like%20what%20to%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223678%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673fc416fa0140cdd564