t%20NDTV's%20Samvidhan%4075%20conclave%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20separation%20of%20power%20between%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20which%20had%20become%20a%20talking%20point%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20of%20appointing%20judges%20is%20very%20nuanced%20and%20multi-layered%2C%20and%20the%20judiciary%20has%20no%20exclusive%20role%20in%20it%2C%20he%20said%2C%20clarifying%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20does%20not%20singlehandedly%20finalise%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20collegium%20system%20has%20entrusted%20responsibility%20to%20different%20levels%20of%20state%20-%20not%20government%20-%20in%20a%20federal%20system.%20It%20involves%20the%20high%20courts%20and%20goes%20past%20state%20and%20central%20executives.%20Not%20just%20the%20centre%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20but%20even%20chief%20ministers%20and%20governors%20send%20their%20inputs%2C%20which%20are%20collated%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20their%20final%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20published%20a%20set%20of%20norms%20for%20appointing%20judges%2C%20which%20include%20the%20judge's%20seniority%20and%20integrity%2C%20the%20need%20for%20representation%20for%20different%20regions%20and%20classes%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-on-social-media-trolling-judges-should-be-trained-7093451%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJudges%20Should%20Be%20Trained%26quot%3B%3A%20DY%20Chandrachud%20On%20Social%20Media%20Trolling%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20alleged%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20process%2C%20he%20highlighted%20the%20dangers%20linked%20to%20it.%20Stating%20that%20the%20process%20deals%20with%20the%20lives%20and%20careers%20of%20judges%2C%20he%20said%20if%20all%20the%20reaso