n.%20He%20referred%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20framing%20guidelines%20for%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20workplace%2C%20which%20was%20in%20force%20until%20the%20parliament%20enacted%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProblems%20may%20also%20arise%20due%20to%20inadequate%20enforcement%20of%20law%2C%20in%20which%20the%20courts%20must%20step%20in%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20say%20this%20is%20a%20policy%20issue%20-%20whether%20to%20shut%20schools%20or%20allow%20trucks%20in%20Delhi.%20But%20apart%20from%20just%20pure%20policy%20issues%2C%20they%20also%20raise%20concerns%20over%20fundamental%20rights.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20courts%20cannot%20step%20aside%20on%20every%20issue%20and%20say%20this%20is%20a%20policy%20matter%20that%20we%20cannot%20decide.%20When%20fundamental%20rights%20are%20involved%2C%20courts%20are%20dutybound%20under%20the%20constitution%20to%20step%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20former%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20how%20regulatory%20agencies%20are%20taking%20over%20the%20core%20function%20of%20courts%20-%20to%20decide%20disputes%20in%20special%20sectors%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20a%20change%20from%20the%20traditional%20idea%20of%20separation%20of%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20separation%20of%20power%20as%20a%20basic%20concept%20of%20democracy%20is%20alive%20and%20well%20in%20our%20society%2C%20but%20changes%20have%20occurred%20due%20to%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20modern%20age%20in%20which%20we%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20for%20two%20years%20ending%20November%2010%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732444860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fmuklbd9g_dy-chandrachud_625x300_24_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshould-appointing-judges-be-more-transparent-dy-chandrachud-explains-7