re%20stocks%20have%20also%20started%20to%20take%20off.%20Data-center%20stocks%20like%20Vertiv%20and%20Digital%20Realty%20have%20soared%20as%20the%20demand%20to%20build%20out%20AI%20capacity%20has%20risen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20so-called%20%26quot%3BPhase%203%26quot%3B%20AI%20stocks%2C%20which%20are%20rolling%20out%20the%20technology%20to%20increase%20their%20revenues%2C%20are%20set%20to%20shine%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2025%20will%20be%20the%20year%20of%20transition%20from%20investing%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20to%20AI%20beneficiaries%2C%20Goldman's%20Chief%20US%20Equity%20Strategist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-outlook-next-decade-forecast-david-kostin-goldman-stocks-strategist-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Kostin%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20Two%20years%20after%20the%20debut%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20more%20and%20more%20revenue-generating%20use%20cases%20for%20AI%20are%20emerging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Phase%202%20stocks%20may%20continue%20to%20outperform%20the%20broad%20equity%20market%2C%20we%20expect%20returns%20will%20be%20earnings-driven%20and%20the%20risk%2Freward%20for%20new%20capital%20appears%20more%20attractive%20within%20Phase%203%2C%26quot%3B%20Kostin%20and%20his%20team%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d1eaa98-ba33-4612-9d35-525a3358a144%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMove%20over%2C%20Magnificent%20Seven%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20incredible%20two-year%20rally%2C%20it's%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20see%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20cooling%20off.%20The%20stocks%20have%20shown%20impressive%20earnings%20growth%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20have%20come%20to%20dominate%20the%20market%2C%20making%20up%20about%2030%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20by%20market%20cap.%20However%2C%20the%20growth%20that%20placed%20them%20there%20isn't%20sustainable%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%20Kostin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20aren't%20solid%20companies.%20Goldman%20still%20expects%20them%20to%20outperform%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20index%20in%202025%2C%20but%20the%20bank%20is%20expecting%20them%20to%20do%20so%20by%20only%207%25.%20For%20context%2C%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20outperformed%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20by%2022%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%20and%2063%25%20in%202023.%20Valuations%20for%20the%20market's%20biggest%20performers%20are%20overripe%3A%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20trade%20at%20a%20forward%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20of%2030x%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20index%20trades%20at%20a%20modest%2019x.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20the%20AI%20Phase%203%20trade%20comes%20in.%20These%20companies%2C%20whose%20revenues%20and%20earnings%20are%20set%20to%20get%20a%20boost%20from%20AI%20implementation%2C%20are%20valued%20much%20more%20reasonably%2C%20with%20the%20typical%20Phase%203%20company%20trading%20at%20only%200.1%20standard%20deviations%20more%20expensive%20than%20average%2C%20compared%20to%200.5%20for%20Phase%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValuations%20for%20Phase%203%20stocks%20are%20depressed%20due%20to%20a%20recent%20decreased%20enthusiasm%20for%20AI%2C%20as%20some%20market%20experts%20have%20been%20questioning%20if%20AI%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-fundamental-issues-pop-goldman-sachs-global-head-equity-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20trillion-dollar%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20ready%20to%20pop%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20expectations%20for%20Phase%203%20stocks%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20these%20companies%20to%20beat%20investor%20expectations%20and%20increase%20their%20share%20price.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-earnings-report-call-live-updates-2024-11%5C