p%3EJay%20Bhattacharya%2C%20a%20Stanford%20University-trained%20physician%20and%20economist%2C%20has%20reportedly%20emerged%20as%20the%20presumptive%20favourite%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20transition%20team%20for%20the%20post%20of%20next%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20(NIH)%2C%20a%20nearly%20USD%2050%20billion%20agency%20that%20oversees%20the%20nation's%20biomedical%20research.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Stanford-trained%20physician%20and%20economist%20met%20this%20week%20with%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.--%20who%20has%20been%20appointed%20by%20Mr%20Trump%20to%20lead%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20(HHS)--%20United%20States'%20top%20health%20agency%20which%20oversees%20NIH%20and%20other%20health%20agencies%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhealth%2F2024%2F11%2F23%2Fbhattacharya-nih-director-trump-candidate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20citing%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20Dr%20Bhattacharya%20impressed%20Kennedy%20with%20his%20ideas%20to%20overhaul%20NIH%20by%20shifting%20the%20agency's%20focus%20toward%20funding%20more%20innovative%20research.%20He%20also%20reportedly%20recommended%20reducing%20the%20influence%20of%20some%20of%20its%20longest-serving%20career%20officials%2C%20among%20other%20ideas.%20NIH%20awards%20funding%20grants%20to%20researchers%2C%20oversees%20clinical%20trials%20on%20its%20Maryland%20campus%2C%20and%20supports%20a%20variety%20of%20efforts%20to%20develop%20drugs%20and%20therapeutics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20transition%20team%20has%20yet%20to%20make%20any%20official%20statement%20regarding%20the%20developments%20being%20reported.%20The%20decision%20of%20who%20will%20lead%20NIH%20will%20not%20be%20final%20until%20the%20President-elect%20himself%20announces%20it%2C%20as%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20known%20to%20sometimes%20rebuff%20his%20advisers'%20recommendations.%20The%20President-elect's%20transition%20team%20has%2C%20reportedly%2C%20also%20looked%20at%20other%20candidates%20to%20lead%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Jay%20Bhattacharya%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20India%2C%20in%201968%2C%20Jayanta%20%26quot%3BJay%26quot%3B%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20Health%20Policy%20at%20Stanford%20University%20and%20a%20research%20associate%20at%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economics%20Research.%20He%20holds%20an%20MD%20and%20PhD%20in%20economics%20--%20both%20earned%20at%20Stanford%20University%20--%20and%20also%20directs%20Stanford's%20Center%20for%20Demography%20and%20Economics%20of%20Health%20and%20Aging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Stanford's%20official%20website%2C%20Dr%20Bhattacharya's%20research%20focuses%20on%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20vulnerable%20populations%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20emphasis%20on%20the%20role%20of%20government%20programs%2C%20biomedical%20innovation%2C%20and%20economics.%20His%20recent%20research%20focuses%20on%20the%20epidemiology%20of%20COVID-19%20as%20well%20as%20an%20evaluation%20of%20policy%20responses%20to%20the%20epidemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economist's%20broader%20research%20interests%20encompass%20the%20implications%20of%20population%20ageing%20for%20future%20population%20health%20and%20medical%20spending%20in%20developed%20countries%2C%20the%20measurement%20of%20physician%20performance%20tied%20to%20physician%20payment%20by%20insurers%2C%20and%20the%20role%20played%20by%20biomedical%20innovation%20on%20health.%20He%20has%20published%20135%20articles%20in%20top%20peer-reviewed%20scientific%20journals%20in%20medicine%2C%20economics%2C%20health%20policy%2C%20epidemiology%2C%20statistics%2C%20law%2C%20and%20public%20health%20among%20other%20fields.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhattacharya%20was%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20federal%20government's%20COVID-19%20response%2C%20co-writing%20an%20October%202020%20open%20letter%20known%20as%20the%20Great%20Barrington%20Declaration%20that%20called%20for%20rolling%20back%20coronavirus-related%20shutdowns%20while%20keeping%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20protections%26quot%3B%20for%20vulnerable%20populations%2C%20such%20as%20older%20Americans.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20proposal%20won%20support%20from%20Republican%20politicians%20and%20some%20Americans%20eager%20to%20resume%20daily%20life%2C%20but%20it%20was%20criticized%20as%20being%20unethical%20and%20infeasible%20by%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%2C%20the%20director-general%20of%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732434780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fuiepa8pg_jay-bhattacharya-twitter_625x300_24_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjay-bhattacharya-born-in-kolkata-emerges-as-trumps-top-pick-to-head-us-health-agency-7093578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jay%20Bhattacharya%2C%20a%20Stanford%20University-trained%20physician%20and%20economist%2C%20has%20reportedly%20emerged%20as%20the%20presumptive%20favourite%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20transition%20team%20for%20the%20post%20of%20next%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20(NIH).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjay-bhattacharya-born-in-kolkata-emerges-as-trumps-top-pick-to-head-us-health-agency-7093578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJudges%20Should%20Be%20Trained%26quot%3B%3A%20DY%20Chandrachud%20On%20Social%20Media%20Trolling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Justice%20Of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20Sunday%20suggested%20that%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%20trolling%2C%20judges%20should%20be%20trained%20to%20handle%20the%20internet.%20He%20also%20quipped%20that%20he%20has%20been%20trolled%20on%20social%20media%20not%20just%20once%2C%20but%20several%20times%20during%20his%20term%20-%20something%20that%20he%20even%20said%20during%20his%20parting%20speech%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20judges%20should%20also%20be%20trained.%20In%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20how%20will%20you%20handle%20the%20internet%2C%20the%20trolling%3F%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20necessary%20for%20all%20the%20judges%20to%20go%20through%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20speaking%20at%20NDTV's%20Samvidhan%20%40%2075%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-australia-vs-india-always-stable-always-solid-dy-chandrachud-praises-this-retired-cricketer-7093211%5C%22%3EChandrachud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20are%20now%20living%20in%20a%20new%20normal%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bpost-truth%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20times%20have%20changed%20now...In%201950%2C%20there%20was%20no%20social%20media%2C%20no%20internet.%20Now%2C%20the%20Constitution%20has%20gone%20through%20the%20process%20of%2075%20years%20of%20evolution.%20We%20are%20now%20living%20in%20a%20new%20normal%20-%20some%20call%20it%20the%20post-truth%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20social%20media%20trolling%20affects%20judges%2C%20Mr%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes..I%20have%20been%20trolled%20on%20social%20media%20not%20once%20but%20several%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funemployed-chief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-parting-dig-at-trolls-6974100%5C%22%3Etroll%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20time%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Chandrachud%2C%20social%20media%20is%20not%20just%20merely%20a%20form%20of%20communication%20but%20also%20a%20powerful%20means%20of%20affecting%20outcomes%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...Because%20obviously%2C%20today%20there%20are%20special%20interest%20groups%2C%20pressure%20groups%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20use%20social%20media%20to%20affect%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20courts%20and%20the%20outcomes%20of%20cases.%20Every%20citizen%20is%20entitled%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20decision%20and%20to%20express%20their%20opinions%20on%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20court.%20But%20when%20this%20goes%20beyond%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20court%20and%20targets%20individual%20judges%2C%20then%20it%20sort%20of%20raises%20fundamental%20questions%20about%20-%20Is%20this%20truly%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20that%20in%20today's%20time%2C%20everybody's%20attention%20span%20on%20social%20media%20is%2020%20seconds%20with%20the%20development%20of%20'shorts'%20-%20short-timed%20videos%20on%20YouTube%2C%20similar%20to%20'reels'%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20I%20watch%20them%20now%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20chuckled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%2C%20therefore%20wants%20to%20form%20an%20opinion%20in%2020%20seconds%20of%20what%20they%20see%20on%20YouTube%20or%20any%20social%20media%20platform.%20This%20poses%20a%20grave%20danger%20because%20the%20process%20of%20decision-making%20in%20the%20courts%20is%20far%20more%20serious.%20It%20is%20really%20nuanced%20that%20nobody%20has%20the%20patience%20or%20the%20tolerance%20today%20on%20social%20media%20to%20understand%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20issue%20that%20is%20confronting%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%20of%20court%20cases%20being%20discussed%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Mr%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJudges%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20constantly%20being%20subject%20to%20this%20barrage%20of%20special%20interest%20groups%20trying%20to%20alter%20the%20decisions%20of%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20courts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20there%20are%20fundamental%20values%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20which%20are%20involved.%20So%20speaking%20for%20my%20speaking%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20have%20been%20a%20proponent%20of%20giving%20the%20maximum%20freedom%20to%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20That's%20really%20what%20the%20Constitution%20is%20all%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732434300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fvoo4e1bo_dyc_625x300_24_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-on-social-media-trolling-judges-should-be-trained-7093451%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chief%20Justice%20Of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20Sunday%20suggested%20that%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%20trolling%2C%20judges%20should%20be%20trained%20to%20handle%20the%20internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-on-social-media-trolling-judges-should-be-trained-7093451%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain%20and%20India%20Talk%20Location%20Production%20and%20Distribution%20Opportunities%20at%20Film%20Bazaar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732434274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSpain-panel-pic-3x2-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236221686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20vast%20expanse%20of%20opportunity%20that%20exists%20if%20India%20and%20Spain%20manage%20to%20increase%20