20able%20to%20operate%20it%20without%20needing%20technical%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20This%20focus%20on%20simplicity%20and%20functionality%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWinning%20the%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20dedication%20and%20tireless%20effort%20have%20certainly%20not%20escaped%20attention.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20she%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20mother%20calling%20me%20and%20telling%20me%20I%20won%20the%20award.%20Words%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20describe%20what%20I%20was%20feeling%20at%20that%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20recalls.%20Suhani%20is%20the%20sole%20recipient%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Innovation%20and%20the%20only%20honoree%20from%20Delhi%20to%20receive%20this%20highest%20National%20Award%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202106px)%20100vw%2C%202106px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222106%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suhani's%20interaction%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20memorable%20for%20her%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716.jpg%202106w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11z